{
  "stem": "23599.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the mothers asked where are our children when we came-- so one of the women, I'll never forget how she asked.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You are asking?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are asking for-- about your children?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You ask where they are?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There are you children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They showed to the chimney.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said to the chimney showed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's where your children are.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Yeah, what else?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You arrived in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We then-- then-- we stayed-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed in bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had the bunk beds, like two in the bunk beds, two.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two on the main and two higher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to-- we went to-- we had to be cleaned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to go to a bathroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were scared there, because we thought that they will-- that this our last day, that they will-- you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But no, they-- we had to wash.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- and we got new dresses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The old-- our dresses, our own, were taken away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they gave us other dresses, but they didn't fit nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were [LAUGHS] not made to measure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were not made to measure that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when-- but we had to wear whatever we got.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then when we were put on those dresses [INAUDIBLE], some women got frantic to see, you know, what they look like in the dress, or a skirt.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they never tried or never wore a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "More-- more or less.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I didn't-- I didn't worry about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We absolutely, we did nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we were [INAUDIBLE]-- afraid, for instance, to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you never know with German camps that they can shoot you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what we had, we were so many women.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
